responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "03C9F5514415C482BFBCD595A545B589", "The Striders Vigilant? Rangers organization. They\'re out there, if you\'re looking for them, sneaking about. They keep an eye on things, comings and goings - try to keep folks out of trouble. They check in on us here from time to time to let us know what\'s going on out there. Not really scholars though, more doers than thinkers in that crowd. I need a cleric\'s eye on those markings before I can come to any strong conclusions.")
